- Identical in every detail.

244
00:15:08,690 --> 00:15:10,489
How much does she weigh?

245
00:15:10,490 --> 00:15:13,059
- 600 kilos.
- But that's crazy.

246
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:15,759
- Why so heavy?
- It's a V12 engine.

247
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:18,829
That lump weighs
190K on its own.

248
00:15:18,830 --> 00:15:19,800
Okay.

249
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:23,469
