262
00:16:16,430 --> 00:16:18,790
Okay, thank you. Good night.

263
00:16:38,810 --> 00:16:41,080
What was Regazzoni's time?

264
00:16:41,950 --> 00:16:43,689
1:53.

265
00:16:43,690 --> 00:16:46,989
