take it for a spin.

272
00:17:03,710 --> 00:17:04,930
Gloves, please.

273
00:17:50,690 --> 00:17:53,519
- I'd say we push it...
- All right.

274
00:17:53,520 --> 00:17:55,789
What did you do to the car?

275
00:17:55,790 --> 00:17:57,629
That's information
I'll share with you

276
00:17:57,630 --> 00:17:59,589
