1234
01:34:49,870 --> 01:34:51,930
<i>James Hunt alongside him.</i>

1235
01:34:53,100 --> 01:34:55,239
<i>On row two of the grid,</i>

1236
01:34:55,240 --> 01:34:56,809
<i>there is Niki Lauda,</i>

1237
01:34:56,810 --> 01:34:59,639
