01:38:18,410 --> 01:38:19,380
No.

1271
01:38:20,510 --> 01:38:21,940
Tell them the truth.

1272
01:38:22,610 --> 01:38:24,509
<i>Now, what is happening?</i>

1273
01:38:24,510 --> 01:38:26,479
<i>They're talking to
the team manager.</i>

1274
01:38:26,480 --> 01:38:28,920
<i>Lauda explaining something.</i>

1275
01:38:43,600 --> 01:38:46,769
<i>With Lauda out, James Hunt
